features: UNIVERSAL TV COMPATIBILITY- Our TV wall mount is compatible with most of 26"-55" TVs with VESA from 75x75mm to 400x400mm. Max. weight capacity up to 66 lbs. The wall mount is compatible with all major TV brands, including Samsung, LG, Sony, TCL, Vizio, Panasonic, Thomson, Toshiba, Sharp etc. Please check the VESA pattern, weight, size of your TV before purchasing. Can be mounted to single wood stud wall and concrete/brick wall.

MULTI VIEWING ANGLE - Tilts TV 5° upward and 15° downward to reduce glare. Swivels TV left or right 90° (max swivel angle depends on TV size) according to your seat position. Extends up to 17 inch and retract back to 2.2 inch allowing a better viewing experience. For full detailed specification see images and description.

STABLE AND RELIABLE CHOICE - This TV bracket is constructed with premium steel materials, Ultra strong arms more sturdy and flexible. It has been stress tested to hold 4 times its weight based on Ul standards. We are so confident in the construction, strength and durability of this wall bracket. It will keep your new TV safe.

QUICK AND EASY INSTALLATION - With complete hardware provided, 1-2-3 simple installation way and friendly detailed English graphical installation guide that is actually useful (and even funny) which helps you to install this full motion TV wall mount without any hassle.

EXCELLENT CUSTOMER SERVICE - Still worry about input blocking? VESA compatibility? it has 4 extender brackets for different VESA range. No idea of the suitable mount, etc. Contact us now and find the perfect TV wall bracket.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s a one size fit all TV wall mount that’s easy to install
reviews.reviewText: I have purchased two of these and each time I think it’s gonna be difficult and it’s easy. The directions are not so good but for the price and sturdiness, it’s makes up for it. Just make sure your TV is under 55 inches and 50 pounds. I have purchased two of these and installed both myself, one on an older flat screen and another on a 43 in newer tv. You just need a good drill stud finder, some patience, a flat surface to mount the bracket on the back of the TV bed is best and a second set of hands helps when you’re lifting the TV into place. I installed my original wall mount 15 years ago, and it took all day 7 hrs this one I did this one in under an hour.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Installation is Incredibly Simple!!!! Great unit!
reviews.reviewText: I don't want to sound harsh, but if this presented significant challenges to install, you may want to consider selling, or donating your tools. This applies only if you received a complete, correct mounting kit, with instructions. A torque wrench is not required, as is asserted in another review, I will assume they meant a "ratchet", and simply said torque. You do need a drill, a 1/8 bit, a small level, pencil, and yes... a stud finder (which can be had for under $10, is incredibly simple to use, and every household needs one (IMHO). The instructions make it clear that this must be mounted to a stud concrete/brick, and cannot be mounted on drywall only. The anchors they provide for concrete resemble drywall anchors, but do not use them as such or your TV wi slowly pull the mount out the wall as is illustrated in another review by someone who did not read the instructions carefully, and attempted to use the concrete anchors as drywall anchors in an application where drywall anchors won't even work. They also paid a professional to help, for which they should receive a full refund. If you fully seat the three provided 10mm lag bolts into a stud (in predrilled 1/8" pot holes) , the mount will not pull out from the weight of a TV that is rated for this mount (I believe the mount would fail long before the lags pulled out of the stud, from excess weight). This is a very sturdy, rugged, easy to install, cersaowall mount, that I highly recommend. This is as easy as it gets mounting something to a wall stud.
This product was delivered fast and installed even faster, basic and easy set up. Solid product for the price
This is the second time I bought this product. I really like it!
Excellent price easy to install and super quick delivery
